We believe that membership has its advantages! That’s why we have made it even more affordable than ever! For about the price of a cup of Starbucks a day, you can join Royal Oaks Golf Club! When you are a member, you can play anytime on any day for only $18+tax! We have two different types of memberships to offer: residents with a private cart pay $1,600 + tax annually, residents without a private cart pay $2,000 + tax annually. If you have any questions, please give us a call at
(352) 861-1818 Ext. #1
and ask for Ed. Cheers!
